### GET demo by id - success (id <= 100)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/1

### GET demo by id - ResourceNotFoundException (id > 100)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/999

### POST process - success
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/process
Content-Type: application/json

"ValidItem"

### POST process - BusinessException (UNPROCESSABLE_ENTITY)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/process
Content-Type: application/json

"INVALID"

### POST validate - success
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/validate
Content-Type: application/json

"TestItem"

### POST validate - IllegalArgumentException (generic 500 error)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/demo/validate
Content-Type: application/json

""